        <item>
        <title>ETSHelper</title>
        <link>http://czzzzh.github.io/p/etshelper/</link>
        <pubDate>Sat, 01 Aug 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>http://czzzzh.github.io/p/etshelper/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="http://czzzzh.github.io/p/etshelper/demo.jpg" alt="Featured image of post ETSHelper" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/CzzzzH/ETSHelper&#34;&gt;https://github.com/CzzzzH/ETSHelper&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;introduction&#34;&gt;Introduction&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The bot is based on &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/howmanybots/onebot&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Nonebot&lt;/a&gt; (A asynchronous framework of QQ chatbot) and &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/Jittor/Jittor&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Jittor&lt;/a&gt; (A Just-in-time(JIT) deep learning framework). The former provides communication services for the bot , and the latter helps crack captcha on the website.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;usage&#34;&gt;Usage&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You need construct dataset with captcha data on the official test registration website and &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://cg.cs.tsinghua.edu.cn/jittor/download/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;install Jittor&lt;/a&gt;. Then train the model.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Start to get GRE/TOEFL test seats status with gre_seat.py / toefl_seat.py. Selenium and mysql is required in this process..&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deploy your own QQ chatbot with software supported by Nonebot.  (e.g. &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/mamoe/mirai&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Mirai&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run bot.py to start the query service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;demo&#34;&gt;Demo&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can add the demo bot (QQ:2758720749) for instant querying service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5 id=&#34;this-bot-is-currently-unavailable-in-terms-of-the-change-of-the-ets-official-website-so-the-bot-and-this-repository-is-waiting-for-update&#34;&gt;This bot is currently unavailable in terms of the change of the ETS official website, so the bot and this repository is waiting for update.&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;!-- raw HTML omitted --&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
